<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>This is a feature request that the Zend_Db_Adapter class should support an interface to allow one to specify a custom class for the Profiler object.  Currently the Adapter is hardcoded to create an instance of 'Zend_Db_Profiler' and there is no way to specify the class, or pass an object instance, or set the Adapter's profiler.</p>

<p>Currently the Adapter configuration options supports a key 'profiler' which if {{true}} means to enable the profiler upon creation of the Adapter.</p>

    </div>
</div>

